# Cursor Rules for 101 Jiu Jitsu Website

## Project Context
- Martial arts gym website for 101 Jiu Jitsu & Kickboxing in Goleta, CA
- Static HTML/CSS/JS site deployed to Vercel
- Mobile-first, responsive design

## Brand Guidelines
- Primary Red: #E42416
- Primary Dark: #C41E1A  
- Secondary (Dark): #0a1628
- Accent Blue: #1e3a8a
- White: #ffffff
- Font: Oswald (headings), Inter (body)

## Component Patterns

### Navigation
```html
<nav class="navbar">
  <div class="nav-container">
    <a href="index.html" class="logo">
      <img src="logo.webp" alt="101 Jiu Jitsu & Kickboxing">
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
      <li class="dropdown">
        <a href="#">Programs ▼</a>
        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
          <li><a href="jiu-jitsu.html">Jiu-Jitsu</a></li>
          <li><a href="kickboxing.html">Kickboxing</a></li>
          <li><a href="boxing.html">Boxing</a></li>
          <li><a href="wrestling.html">Wrestling</a></li>
          <li><a href="kids-teens.html">Kids/Teens</a></li>
          <li><a href="mma-gym.html">MMA</a></li>
          <li><a href="trx-training.html">TRX</a></li>
          <li><a href="rocksteady.html">Rocksteady</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="instructors.html">Instructors</a></li>
      <li><a href="class-schedule.html">Schedule</a></li>
      <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
      <li><a href="free-trial.html" class="nav-cta">Free Trial</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>
```

### Hero Section
```html
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <h1>SEO-RICH H1 TITLE</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Compelling description with keywords</p>
    <a href="free-trial.html" class="btn btn-primary">CTA Button</a>
  </div>
</section>
```

### Buttons
- `.btn-primary` - Red background, white text
- `.btn-secondary` - Transparent, white border
- `.btn-white` - White background, dark text (for dark sections)

## SEO Requirements
- Every page needs unique H1 with keywords
- Meta title: 50-60 characters with location
- Meta description: 150-160 characters
- Schema markup for LocalBusiness on contact page

## File Structure
```
101-jjkb-site/
├── index.html (homepage)
├── about.html
├── free-trial.html (dedicated page)
├── contact.html (with maps + schema)
├── class-schedule.html
├── instructors.html
├── Program pages:
│   ├── jiu-jitsu.html
│   ├── kickboxing.html
│   ├── boxing.html
│   ├── wrestling.html
│   ├── kids-teens.html
│   ├── mma-gym.html
│   ├── rocksteady.html
│   └── trx-training.html
├── System pages:
│   ├── thank-you.html
│   ├── 404.html
│   ├── privacy.html
│   └── terms.html
├── css/
│   └── styles.css (shared styles)
├── js/
│   └── main.js (shared scripts)
└── images/
```

## Interactive Features Needed
1. Mobile menu toggle
2. Dropdown navigation on hover/click
3. Smooth scroll for anchor links
4. Scroll animations (fade-in, slide-up)
5. Form validation
6. Image lazy loading

