## Quality Checks
- [ ] Consistent navigation on ALL pages
- [ ] Proper spacing and margins
- [ ] Mobile responsive
- [ ] All links work
- [ ] Images optimized and unique per page
- [ ] SEO meta tags present
- [ ] Schema markup on contact
- [ ] Fast loading (< 3s)
